Welcome to Atonement RPI! 

Atonement is a Role-Playing Intensive MUD, and uses an account system to keep
track of your characters and any awards or achievements you accrue over your
playing history. To start playing, you will first need to create an account
by nomimating an account name and a valid email address, and then create a
character with which to engage with the post-apocalyptic sci-fi horror
world that awaits.


